---
title: Turkish Lamb & Feta Pide with Chopped Cucumber & Radish Salad
description: Ready for an unforgettable culinary adventure? This radiant pide will transport you straight to the bustling streets of Istanbul,
with a warmly spiced lamb and onion filling cradled within golden dough and sprinkled with tangy, creamy feta. Let’s dig right in!
